description:
Nonsense(cial)

CONTROLS N STUFF IDC:

Arrow keys = Singing poses

1 = Switch to Normal Nonsense

2 = Switch to Worried Nonsense

3 = Switch to Mad Nonsense

4 = Switch to Angry Nonsense

5 = Switch to God Mode Nonsense

SPACE = Skip Cutscene

Z = Animation 1

X = Animation 2

X = Explode animation (Only for Phase 5)

E= Next song
